@node "kurz" "short overview"
This program allowed to make plots from given x/y datas. You can link the
points with different modes (nothing, line, spline) and apply some @{"statistic" link "statistik" 0}
functions (like regression, median, mean etc.) on the datas.

@endnode

@node "req" "Requirements"
@{CODE}
  - WB 3.0 or better (should not be any problem)
  - at least 1 MByte RAM (more recommended!)
  - iff.library 2.0
@{BODY}

@endnode

